value: Amazon river islands (ne Ecuador to n Bolivia and w Brazil)

Eastern Ecuador (?); northeastern Peru on the lower Napo (mouth of the Rio Curaray; Puerto Indiana) and the Rio Ucayali (Santa Rosa; Lagarto); Brazil on the Rio Madeira (Borba) and the Rio Mamore (Santo Antonio de Guajara); northeastern Bolivia in Department of Beni (Reyes).
